  "date": "2026-03-03",
  "notes": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Corruption Risk Mapping<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm;text-align:center\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Interview Report<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"711\" style=\"width:533.3pt;\n mso-cellspacing:1.5pt;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184\">\n <tbody><tr>\n  <td width=\"129\" style=\"width:96.95pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Item</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Details</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"129\" style=\"width:96.95pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Date\n  of interview</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">March 3, 2026<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"129\" style=\"width:96.95pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewee</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Anke BALCAEN<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"129\" style=\"width:96.95pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Function</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Marketing Director &amp;\n  Responsible for Scientific Information – Belgium, Netherlands, Luxembourg<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"129\" style=\"width:96.95pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewers</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td style=\"border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;\n  padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Antoine LASSAUGE, Sandra LASAGNI<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#0070C0;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US\">1. Perimeter of responsibilities and activities<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Department / Function</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Marketing\n      Director</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n      115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> and <b>Responsible for Scientific\n      Information</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Dual\n      role combining <b>marketing</b>, <b>customer scientific communication</b>,\n      and <b>support to field teams</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Geographical\n     scope:</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n     115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Belgium</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Netherlands</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Luxembourg</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Responsibilities</span></b><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">:<o:p></o:p></span></b></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Leads <b>marketing\n      strategy</b> for the three countries.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Ensures\n      <b>scientific information</b> is provided to healthcare professionals\n      (HCPs), including physicians, pharmacists and nurses.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Maintains\n      relationships with <b>patient associations</b>, primarily in hematology.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Team structure: </span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">supervises: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">A team\n      of <b>SPAs (Scientific Product Advisors)</b> who have a hybrid\n      scientific/commercial role and are in daily contact with HCPs.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Key\n      Account Managers</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">, reporting to the Sales\n      Manager.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Internal\n      marketing team</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">, working on promotional\n      materials without HCP contact.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Main missions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Annual <b>medical-marketing\n      planning</b> by product and country.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Definition\n      and approval of <b>field action plans</b> (“call plans”) including: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Prioritisation\n       of hospitals and HCPs,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Targeting\n       rules (minimum number of HCPs, minimum contact frequency),<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Manager\n       validation and cross-check by the person in charge of targeting.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">KOL mapping</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> based on: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Past year’s HCO sales,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Upcoming tender opportunities,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Hospital size and influence.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Management\n      of <b>international congress participation</b>, including selection of\n      HCPs to invite.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Selection\n      and contractual management of <b>Hemosims ambassadors</b> for educational\n      simulation sessions.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Annual\n      preparation of <b>budget and supervision of patient association support</b>\n      (one association in Belgium and one in the Netherlands).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Oversight\n      of <b>scientific information dissemination</b> and interactions with\n      KOLs.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\npage-break-after:avoid\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n115%;color:#0070C0;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">2. Third parties, nature of interactions,\nrisks and controls<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.1. Healthcare Professionals (HCPs)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Frequent\n      face‑to‑face hospital visits (preferred interaction).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Emails\n      and other remote contacts.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Organization\n      of <b>staff meetings</b> (group training or product-related sessions).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Presence at congress booths.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Invitations\n      to <b>international congresses</b> (mostly) with full internal\n      validation.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Facilitation\n      of <b>Advisory Board participation</b> organized by HQ.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Frequency / volume</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Daily\n      interactions by field teams.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Congress:\n      limited number due to strict budget and justification rules.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Annual\n      targeting plan with minimum required number of HCP interactions.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Corruption risks discussed</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">HCPs\n      requesting advantages not allowed (e.g., inviting family members to\n      congresses).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Undue\n      influence of tender processes through invitations or benefits.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk of\n      being asked for favors in exchange for prescriptions (even if it has not\n      happened).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Strict Mdeon rules (Belgium).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Internal\n      validation of HCP invitations.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Transparent documentation of\n      participants and costs.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Field\n      team trainings on anti-bribery.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Clear\n      processes for HR-related solicitations.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">2.2.\nHemosims Ambassadors (contracted HCPs)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Delivering\n      of educational simulation sessions (PPH, trauma, cardio) in their\n      hospital or others (Hemosims).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Contractual\n      remuneration per session with hourly rate covering: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">preparation,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">delivery,<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">debrief.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Frequency</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Regular\n      sessions throughout the year.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks discussed</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk of\n      paying for sessions that did not occur.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk of\n      paying for preparation not actually performed.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Undue\n      influence in peer hospitals.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">SPA\n      and/or Marketing director’s presence during most sessions.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">QR code\n      attendance tracking and satisfaction surveys.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Post-session\n      follow‑up with ambassadors.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Standardized\n      hourly rates preventing inflation.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.3. Patient Associations<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">National\n     hemophilia and Von Willebrand associations in Belgium and the Netherlands.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Annual\n      financial support for one clear project (e.g., symposium, communication\n      platform).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Associations\n      proactively request support each year.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Distribution\n      of patient information materials.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Frequency</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Once annually per association.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Identified risks</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk of\n      sponsoring projects perceived as buying influence.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Risk of\n      excessive or unjustified financial support.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Mandatory\n      approval by the <b>International Project Validation Committee</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Fixed\n      annual budget and selection of only one project per association.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Clear justification and\n      transparency.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.4. Hospitals – Tender Processes<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Information\n      gathering <b>before</b> tender publication (authorised).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No\n      contact allowed</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n      line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> after publication (Belgium\n      BOSA system).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Frequency</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Continuous\n      monitoring of tender publications (BOSA daily notifications).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Risks discussed</span></b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Attempt\n      to obtain confidential information.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Attempt\n      to influence tender specifications.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Potential\n      perception of undue favour through HCP relations.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Public\n      transparency of tender publication (BOSA).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Strict\n      internal rules: zero contact once tender published.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Sales Manager oversight.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Anti-corruption\n      trainings emphasising tender risks.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.5. Government / Public Institutions<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Contact\n     mainly managed by the Managing Director.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No\n     specific risk identified.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.6. Recruitment / Internships<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No\n     internship program in Belgium, but potential risk exists if an HCP\n     requests a job or internship for a relative.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">HR\n     handles all recruitment independently of operational managers.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>",
